om/card/fin/256/elixir?utm_source=api", "local": "img/elixir/3e978db3-77ef-4b93-8f8f-e414e27254bd.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Reviving Dose", "set": "CN2", "html": "Samite healers never mix their pungent <mark>elixir</mark> with sweetener or tea. The threat of a second dose is enough to get most warriors back on their feet.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/a/9a2b2de2-7427-42df-b6ad-b159a0f6a13a.jpg?1782711744"}, {"card": "Revitalize", "set": "KHM", "html": "Esika alone knows how to distill the essence of the World Tree into the Cosmos <mark>Elixir</mark>, a magical substance which grants the Skoti god-family immortality.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/a/3a9fb75e-c8e5-417b-83d4-5105af9c66c1.jpg?1782705536"}, {"card": "Magic Pot", "set": "FIN", "html": "&quot;Gimme <mark>elixir</mark>!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/7/57d07ca0-5618-4a90-a605-ca14a193ce3b.jpg?1782686392"}, {"card": "Cosmos Elixir", "set": "KHM", "html": "The Skoti owe their immortality to the <mark>elixir</mark>, and the manner of its creation is their most closely guarded secret.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/b/6bf084fe-7762-49c5-974a-cdecc10666b3.jpg?1782705412"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Tzaangor Shaman", "set": "40K", "html": "Flying\nSorcerous <mark>Elixir</mark> — Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player, copy the next instant or sorcery spell you cast this turn when you cast it. You may choose new targets for the copy."}, {"card": "Essence Bottle", "set": "TMP", "html": "{3}, {T}: Put an <mark>elixir</mark> counter on this artifact.\n{T}, Remove all <mark>elixir</mark> counters from this artifact: You gain 2 life for each <mark>elixir</mark> counter removed this way."}, {"card": "Refreshing Elixir", "set": "TBTH", "html": "Hero&#x27;s Reward — When Refreshing <mark>Elixir</mark> is put into a graveyard from anywhere, each player gains 5 life."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/7/b7b8c9d1-34a2-4754-904a-c7d061a6ce0a.jpg?1782700070", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/b/7/b7b8c9d1-34a2-4754-904a-c7d061a6ce0a.jpg?1782700070", "card": "Tzaangor Shaman"}}